{"products":[{"id":7330003386471,"title":"Rhinestone Star Power Jean","handle":"rhinestone-star-power-jean-special-edition","body_html":"\u003cp data-start=\"105\" data-end=\"181\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"138\" data-end=\"181\"\u003eShine Like You Were Born to Stand Out ⭐\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"183\" data-end=\"508\"\u003eUnleash your inner star with our \u003cstrong data-start=\"216\" data-end=\"246\"\u003eRhinestone Star Power Jean\u003c\/strong\u003e — where edgy meets glam in the boldest way possible. These jeans aren’t just denim; they’re a statement. Featuring eye-catching rhinestone star embellishments, this pair is designed to turn sidewalks into runways and everyday moments into main character energy.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"510\" data-end=\"522\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"510\" data-end=\"522\"\u003eDetails:\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"525\" data-end=\"582\"\u003ePremium stretch denim for a flattering, comfortable fit\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"585\" data-end=\"643\"\u003eGlittering rhinestone star accents that demand attention\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"646\" data-end=\"689\"\u003eClassic 5-pocket design with modern flair\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"749\" data-end=\"796\"\u003eDurable and machine-wash safe on gentle cycle\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"798\" data-end=\"963\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"798\" data-end=\"812\"\u003eStyle Tip:\u003c\/strong\u003e Rock it with a crop top, graphic tee, or blazer for that effortless glam-street vibe. Add heels or sneakers — either way, you’re the star of the show.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"965\" data-end=\"1004\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"965\" data-end=\"1002\"\u003eDare to shine. Own the spotlight.\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","published_at":"2025-07-07T14:16:41-04:00","created_at":"2025-07-07T14:16:39-04:00","updated_at"